td.p:
Article 29 of the Agreement on the European Economic Area of 2 May 1992 (
OJ 1994 L 1, p. 3
) provides:

Annex VI to the Agreement on the European Economic Area, as amended by the Decision of the EEA Joint Committee No 76/2011, of 1 July 2011 (
OJ 2011 L 262, p. 33
), refers, in point I, entitled ‘General social security coordination’, to Regulation No 883/2004 and its subsequent amendments.
